```plantuml
@startuml staples-sparx_Wonko
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam linetype ortho

actor "User"
rectangle "Wonko" {
  component "core.clj" as Core
  component "web_server.clj" as WebServer
  component "alert.clj" as Alert
  component "config.clj" as Config
  component "kafka/admin.clj" as KafkaAdmin
  component "kafka/consume.clj" as KafkaConsume
  component "kafka/produce.clj" as KafkaProduce
  component "export/prometheus.clj" as Prometheus
}

component "Kafka" as Kafka
component "Prometheus" as PrometheusSystem
component "PagerDuty" as PagerDuty

User --> WebServer : Access HTTP endpoint
WebServer --> Prometheus : Expose metrics
WebServer --> Core : Initiate processes
Core --> KafkaConsume : Start consuming
KafkaConsume --> Kafka : Consume events
KafkaProduce --> Kafka : Publish alerts
Kafka --> KafkaConsume
Kafka --> KafkaProduce
KafkaConsume --> Alert : Process events
Alert --> PagerDuty : Send notifications
Prometheus --> PrometheusSystem : Register metrics
PrometheusSystem --> Prometheus : Scrape data
@enduml
```